# 🚀 PROJECT OVERVIEW

The **LLM-Assisted Smart Policing System** is an AI-driven analytical platform designed to modernize policing operations using:

- 🧠 Large Language Models (LLMs)
- 📊 Machine Learning Algorithms
- 📝 Natural Language Processing
- 🌐 Web-Based Administrative Dashboard

The system assists law enforcement agencies in:

- Predicting crime categories
- Classifying incident reports
- Extracting intelligence from textual crime descriptions
- Improving decision-making and investigation workflows

---

# 🎯 CORE OBJECTIVES

✅ Smart Crime Prediction  
✅ NLP-Based Incident Analysis  
✅ AI-Assisted Report Classification  
✅ Intelligent Crime Categorization  
✅ Administrative Monitoring Dashboard  
✅ Data-Driven Police Intelligence  

