# 🧪 MACHINE LEARNING MODELS

The system integrates multiple machine learning and NLP models for comparison and performance evaluation.

| Model | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Logistic Regression | Crime Classification |
| KNN | Pattern-Based Prediction |
| SVM | Multi-Class Classification |
| BERT | NLP Contextual Analysis |
| GPT-3 | LLM Feature Extraction |
| XLNet | Advanced Text Understanding |

---

# 🌐 ADMIN DASHBOARD

The platform includes an intelligent web dashboard for:

- Managing police station data
- Uploading incident reports
- Predicting crime categories
- Monitoring prediction results
- Viewing analytical insights

