# 🚀 HOW TO RUN THE PROJECT

# 🖥️ 1️⃣ Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/AJAY29082004/A-Framework-for-LLM-Assisted-Smart-Policing-System.git
```

---

# 📂 2️⃣ Move into Project Folder

```bash
cd A-Framework-for-LLM-Assisted-Smart-Policing-System
```

---

# 🧠 3️⃣ Create Environment (Recommended: Anaconda)

```bash
conda create -n smartpolice python=3.10 -y
```

```bash
conda activate smartpolice
```

---

# 📦 4️⃣ Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

If `requirements.txt` is missing, manually install:

```bash
pip install flask scikit-learn joblib mysql-connector-python transformers
```

---

# ▶️ 5️⃣ Start Application

```bash
cd "FRONT END"
python app.py
```

---

# 🌐 6️⃣ Open in Browser

```text
http://localhost:5000
```

---

# ⚠️ IMPORTANT NOTES

- MySQL must be running locally
- Configure correct database credentials in `app.py`
- Ensure trained ML models are available inside the `models/` directory
- Internet may be required for GPT API access

